dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures, spot heights, and contours. Depth shown by soundings. Routes of expedition shown in red. From: Geographical Journal. Vol. 59, no. 5 (May 1922), pp. 321-334; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J6874
